How to judge if something is worth it?
How much utlity you derive from it? Does it enhance your quality of life?
How much did it cost to produce?
What is the markup/profit margin?
How much joy do you get from using it?
Is it branded?
Does is “pay” for itself?
Was it ethically produced?
How much do similarly priced items cost?

One of the hardest things someone can ask you is if something you bought is worth it. Let me save you some time: there is never a right answer. 

